<h1>Tourism</h1>

<p>Below you may find some suggestions of tourism destinations for your visit. Information on several other destinations can be found at <a href="http://www.visitbrasil.com/en/">Visit Brasil website</a>. In case you need any clarification on the information below, please contact Mr. Rodrigo Mansilha (<a href="rbmansilha@inf.ufrgs.br">rbmansilha@inf.ufrgs.br</a>).

<h2>Fernando de Noronha</h2>

<p><b>Distance to Florian&oacute;polis</b>: 3,133 Km.</p>

<div align="center">
  <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fernando_de_Noronha#/media/File:EDUARDO_MURUCI_-_PRAIA_DO_CACHORRO.jpg"><img src="images/tourism/noronha/praia-cachorro.jpg" alt="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fernando_de_Noronha#/media/File:EDUARDO_MURUCI_-_PRAIA_DO_CACHORRO.jpg" width="625px"></img></a><br/>
  
  <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Fernando_de_Noronha_-_PE_-_Baia_do_Sancho.jpg"><img src="images/tourism/noronha/baia-sancho-beach.jpg" class="img" alt="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Fernando_de_Noronha_-_PE_-_Baia_do_Sancho.jpg" width="400px" height="200px" ></img></a>
  <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Fernando_de_Noronha_-_PE_-_Baia_do_Sancho_-_Sub_Aquatica.jpg"><img src="images/tourism/noronha/baia-sancho.jpg" class="img" alt="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Fernando_de_Noronha_-_PE_-_Baia_do_Sancho_-_Sub_Aquatica.jpg" width="400px" height="200px" ></img></a>

  <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Fernando_de_Noronha_-_dois_Irm%C3%A3os_-_praia_do_sancho.jpg"><img src="images/tourism/noronha/aerial-view.jpg" class="img" alt="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Fernando_de_Noronha_-_dois_Irm%C3%A3os_-_praia_do_sancho.jpg" width="400px" height="200px" ></img></a>
  <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Fernando_de_Noronha_-_PE_-_Dois_Irm%C3%A3os.jpg"><img src="images/tourism/noronha/dois-irmaos.jpg" class="img" alt="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Fernando_de_Noronha_-_PE_-_Dois_Irm%C3%A3os.jpg" width="400px" height="200px" ></img></a>

  <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Ponta_da_Sapata.jpg"><img src="images/tourism/noronha/ponta-sapata.jpg" class="img" alt="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Ponta_da_Sapata.jpg" width="400px" height="200px" ></img></a>
